697757e5-37e4-48cc-825c-d65c4f0e02f6.itemDescription: Iceberg lettuce with tomatoes, chicken, wheat bread croutons, and parmesan cheese. Dressed with Caesar sauce (210g).

7a201000-2af6-4a79-9419-d44f55496bed.itemDescription: Germans were so fond of the tombiks, that invented their own youth version of the rich snack - in addition to meat in Turkish bun, we also add cheese, and French fries. Super rich snack for real youth (430g).

50226bf6-0eb1-40a2-bc54-a42e50c548ff.itemDescription: Lula kebab with delicate turkey, marinated onions, tomatoes, and mix of salads with red sauce. Served in flat bread (260g).

9eee530f-c5bc-4223-b728-608dde419e80.itemDescription: Durum in flat bread with whitefish, cream cheese, mix of vegetables, and white sauce (270g).

9fc0d8e7-9818-4cf3-9805-5e3b7ffec21f.itemDescription: The tombik invented in the 1970s in Berlin by Turkish emigrant Kadir Nurman. Doner veal meat served in a lightly toasted triangle- shaped kefir bun with vegetables, and sauce. Taste of Berlin right now (360g).

5b4ae395-355a-487b-93a7-85970976f77c.title: Durum Doner Caesar

4854140d-894a-40bd-86ea-1013cc425feb.title: Burger Arizona
4854140d-894a-40bd-86ea-1013cc425feb.itemDescription:
Наш єдиний та унікальний справжній американець у меню. Аризона це бургер з великою
соковитою телячою котлетою з сиром та міксом салату. Цікава деталь - ви ніколи не вгадаєте -
який колір булки вам дістанеться - це сюрприз (250 грамів).
